事委员会预期的 1943 年商船建造量是 1600 万吨，那年美国实际建造了 1920 万吨。1943 年 1 月，伯利恒船厂在 46.3 天内建造了 3 艘自由轮，而里士满船厂在 37.5 天内竟建造了 13 艘自由轮。在 1941 年到 1945 年间，18 个美国船坞共计建造了 2751 艘自由轮（如果算上为其他盟国建造的数量的话，总计建造了 5000 多艘）。还有「胜利轮」，胜利轮是在原先自由轮的基础上设计的，整个二战期间一共建造了 531 艘。其建造速度比德国潜艇快多了，任何战术在这样巨大的国力差距面前都不起作用!"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3c29676174307cfc68677e3ca6766191_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "25 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/31003394"}}, "attached_info": "CjwI64OyxODWnchUEAMaBzQ1ODM5NDcgv/DHqwUwADhlQAhyCDMxMDAzMzk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1737420341.356802", "card_id": "Q_21418214", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "二战期间日本有组建特种部队么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在各种抗日雷剧中，不断提到抗日战争期间日本特种部队在华活动。那么在二战期间日本是否真正组建过特种部队，编制及其战例？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-413f6b1e305eb29b278836d88a44eae7_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21418214"}}, "attached_info": "CjsI64OyxODWnchUEAMaBjc0ODAwNCCotOyPBTAAOCVACXIIMjE0MTgyMTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1737420341.357089", "card_id": "Q_10064513622", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 388}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待特朗普提出的「拯救 TikTok 方案」，建立合资企业，其中美国占股 50% ？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "特朗普 19 日早些时候在社交媒体上发文，呼吁各公司不要让 TikTok 处于停止运转状态。特朗普说，他将于 20 日发布一项行政令推迟 TikTok「不卖就禁用」的法律生